@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_cibyra(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.47
    v1 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.78 + v2 + 0.48)) + ((v2 + 0.74 / v1 + 0.68) - (v0 + 0.15 / v2 + 0.85)))
    tmp = v1
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.55 + v2 + 0.83)))
    data[tid] = v0
